Workflow

Load Excel file using openpyxl

Scan first N rows (default = 30)

Compute weighted score per row

Select row with highest score

Load dataframe using detected header

Example Usage
header_line = detect_header_row("file.xlsx")
df = pd.read_excel("file.xlsx", header=header_line - 1)

⚠ Note: openpyxl uses 1-based indexing, while pandas uses 0-based indexing.

